<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Café Tea Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f5f2;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Café Tea Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Black Teas</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>English Breakfast Tea <span>₹230</span></h3>
            <p>A robust black tea blend, perfect with milk and sugar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Earl Grey Tea <span>₹350</span></h3>
            <p>A fragrant black tea infused with citrusy bergamot oil.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Darjeeling Tea <span>₹330</span></h3>
            <p>A musky, floral black tea known as the "champagne of teas."</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Green & White Teas</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Green Tea <span>₹240</span></h3>
            <p>A delicate tea with a grassy, slightly bitter taste, often enjoyed with honey or lemon.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Jasmine Tea <span>₹330</span></h3>
            <p>A delicate green tea infused with fragrant jasmine flowers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>White Tea <span>₹270</span></h3>
            <p>A light, naturally sweet tea made from young tea leaves.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Herbal Teas</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chamomile Tea <span>₹3000</span></h3>
            <p>A soothing herbal tea with a floral flavor, great for relaxation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Peppermint Tea <span>₹130</span></h3>
            <p>A cooling herbal tea that aids digestion and refreshes the senses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Rooibos Tea <span>₹400</span></h3>
            <p>A caffeine-free herbal tea with hints of vanilla and honey.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Lemon Balm Tea <span>₹350</span></h3>
            <p>A soothing herbal tea with a mild lemony flavor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Hibiscus Tea <span>₹2330</span></h3>
            <p>A tangy and vibrant tea made from dried hibiscus flowers.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Specialty Teas</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Oolong Tea <span>₹230</span></h3>
            <p>A complex tea with floral, fruity, or roasted flavors.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Chai Tea <span>₹430</span></h3>
            <p>A warm Indian spiced tea blend with black tea, cinnamon, and cardamom.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Matcha Tea <span>₹550</span></h3>
            <p>A vibrant green powdered tea with a rich, umami flavor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
